  "content": "<p data-pid=\"YTMbpcrL\">另见<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z49u8mtc9wZoY7siV7nz4V3PG2oMkNBn7AgUk\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">合意困难，来自 Bjork</a><sup data-text=\"Bjork ：「上帝啊，这个困难正合我意」——  合意困难\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/490699755\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup></p><p data-pid=\"hkPlm6s3\">关于一个活跃的兴趣领域，见：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2a8QGPfUmdLCVokLaegNzmaU6ehC58CUtYi\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">提取练习和迁移学习</a><sup data-text=\"提取练习和迁移学习\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/536670074\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>。</p><hr/><h2>参考文献</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"HV7D89Ab\">Reder, L., &amp; Klatzky, R. L. (1994). Transfer: Training for performance. In D. Druckman &amp; R. A. Bjork (Eds.), Learning, Remembering, Believing: Enhancing Human Performance (pp. 25–56). National Academies Press. <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.17226/2303\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">doi.org/10.17226/2303</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></li></ul><h3>准备读：</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"wQ7ioJu-\"> Barnett, S. M., &amp; Ceci, S. J. (2002). When and where do we apply what we learn? A taxonomy for far transfer. Psychological Bulletin, 128(4), 612–637. <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.1037/0033-2909.128.4.612\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">doi.org/10.1037/0033-29</span><span class=\"invisible\">09.128.4.612</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"D1wSSKun\"> Gick, M. L., &amp; Holyoak, K. J. (1987). The Cognitive Basis of Knowledge Transfer. In Transfer of Learning (pp. 9–46). Elsevier. <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.1016/B978-0-12-188950-0.50008-4\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">doi.org/10.1016/B978-0-</span><span class=\"invisible\">12-188950-0.50008-4</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><br/> </li></ul><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"uXIxPdK1\"><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/412876669\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">助记媒介可以通过简单的应用卡片帮助读者应用他们所学的知识</a></li><li data-pid=\"I5Xsq_Bi\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/490699755\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Bjork：合意困难</a></li><li data-pid=\"3My9bOl_\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/536670074\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">提取练习和迁移学习</a></li><li data-pid=\"szZp5tkG\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/573838070\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">迁移恰当加工</a></li><li data-pid=\"ThAibAz5\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/677786105\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">人们经常难以回忆起文本的细节，原因在于他们起初就根本没有加工文本</a></li><li data-pid=\"-oYbtbYa\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678612702\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">阅读理解问题可以发现文本基础的漏洞</a></li><li data-pid=\"SeFJ6SIJ\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/697335410\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">认知学徒制</a></li><li data-pid=\"1-dIqI26\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1916570545358627430\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">认知负荷理论</a></li><li data-pid=\"w5woj8uT\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936721806074545452\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">Anderson, J. R., Reder, L. M., &amp; Simon, H. A. (1996)：《情境学习与教育》</a></li><li data-pid=\"PhHDP4vR\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1938891290516390556\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">锚定教学法</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"EXe-X8pe\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"qeViQcKW\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a>汉化组译制<br/>题图：あだしま by 2015chaosgroup<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2hEyCHQpB6UV8z4mYvto7FJud4zWVqZqfxJZ\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Transfer learning (andymatuschak.org)</a></blockquote>",
